  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Fighter Bays provide facilities for manufacture, storage
  and repair of star fighters and bombers aboard ships or bases.<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Once built into a ship or base, fighter bays can build =
new fighters
  and repair existing fighters. No addtional resources or money are require=
d to
  build fighters.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Each fighter bay can build and support four fighters or
  bombers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Higher technology level fighter bays build and repair
  fighters at a faster rate.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
